        "richtext_qYJqTr": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>LitterLens uses a model trained on a diverse dataset of cat and litter box scenes, ensuring that it performs accurately in real-world conditions. The AI has been rigorously tested for:<br/><br/><strong>- High Detection Accuracy:</strong> LitterLens has achieved a high mAP (mean Average Precision) score of 0.85 on the test set, ensuring accurate tracking of your cat’s litter habits.</p><p><strong>- Real-World Testing: </strong>The model has been validated in varied environments, ensuring that it works reliably even in challenging lighting conditions or busy backgrounds.</p>"
          }
        },
